310
00:20:25,780 --> 00:20:27,730
that exists on earth to control me.

314
00:20:52,010 --> 00:20:55,590
The trick to making shakes is to split them...

315
00:20:56,010 --> 00:20:58,850
Not chopped or sawed, but to split.

316
00:20:59,700 --> 00:21:00,530
Thank you.

317
00:21:09,010 --> 00:21:09,770
Your turn.

318
00:21:16,390 --> 00:21:17,800
Right! Well done.

319
00:21:18,650 --> 00:21:19,430
Captain.

320
00:21:22,360 --> 00:21:23,330
Mrs. Sibley.

321
00:21:25,090 --> 00:21:25,990
Young man.

322
00:21:27,470 --> 00:21:29,830
Why don't you go see if there's any fresh water.

323
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:38,330
Big doings this morning.

324
00:21:38,330 --> 00:21:41,310
Seems every day brings its fair share of surprises.

325
00:21:41,310 --> 00:21:43,700
I heard old Increase took possession of your husband.

326
00:21:43,700 --> 00:21:45,060
Yes, he did.

327
00:21:45,060 --> 00:21:46,590
And I'm eager to get him back.

328
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:48,300
You are?

329
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:51,770
Why?

330
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:55,910
