331
00:21:55,910 --> 00:21:58,240
for a wife to want her husband at home?

332
00:21:59,040 --> 00:22:01,640
In most cases, it's not unusual at all.

333
00:22:02,550 --> 00:22:04,970
I heard my hard worker was thirsty.

334
00:22:05,420 --> 00:22:06,810
Oh, Mrs. Sibley.

335
00:22:06,890 --> 00:22:08,860
Uh, fresh apple water on offer.

336
00:22:08,930 --> 00:22:10,630
No, thank you, Anne.

337
00:22:10,970 --> 00:22:12,080
Good day, captain. 

338
00:22:12,430 --> 00:22:13,360
Young man.

339
00:22:17,110 --> 00:22:17,950
Captain.

342
00:22:49,220 --> 00:22:50,010
May I?

343
00:23:30,750 --> 00:23:33,950
