It's not a po--

578
00:36:51,200 --> 00:36:52,340
Look at me, boy.

579
00:36:52,340 --> 00:36:53,740
It's -- it's medicine.

580
00:36:53,740 --> 00:36:55,050
One more time.

581
00:36:56,510 --> 00:37:00,030
I'm going to ask you, who gave it to you?

582
00:37:00,370 --> 00:37:02,680
Master spider, stilted or stifled,

583
00:37:02,680 --> 00:37:05,090
Spin us a web and heed our call.

584
00:37:05,090 --> 00:37:07,750
Master spider, stilted or stifled...

585
00:37:07,930 --> 00:37:09,750
What we'll do is this --

586
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:12,930
It's medicine.

587
00:37:13,850 --> 00:37:15,840
I'm going to slit your belly open.

588
00:37:15,910 --> 00:37:17,050
It's medicine.

589
00:37:17,050 --> 00:37:19,230
I'm going to reach in, pull out,

590
00:37:19,230 --> 00:37:21,920
and I'm going to throttle you with your own intestines.

591
00:37:21,920 --> 00:37:22,950
...heed our call.

592
00:37:22,950 --> 00:37:25,530
Master spider, stilted or stifled,

593
00:37:25,530 --> 00:37:27,740
Spin us a web and heed our call.

594
00:37:27,740 --> 00:37:30,430
Master spider, stilted or stifled...

595
00:37:30,430 --> 00:37:31,930
No. No. No.

596
00:37:31,930 --> 00:37:34,000
Now, you tell me right now,

597
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,550
who gave it to you?!

598
00:37:36,630 --> 00:37:38,140
Tell me, Isaac!

599
00:37:39,140 --> 00:37:40,360
Tell me!

600
00:37:41,140 --> 00:37:44,400
Mrs. Sibley could bring no harm to a living thing.

601
00:37:45,070 --> 00:37:47,210
If -- if she provided me the medicine,

602
00:37:47,210 --> 00:37:48,710
that's good enough for me.

603
00:37:54,130 --> 00:37:55,520
Mrs. Sibley, eh?

604
00:37:57,980 --> 00:37:59,040
Well done.

605
00:38:01,080 --> 00:38:02,230
Off with you now.

606
00:38:07,580 --> 00:38:08,510
Go.

607
00:38:08,990 --> 00:38:11,260
Go on! Out of my sight!

608
00:38:11,500 --> 00:38:14,360
Isaac the fornicator!

609
00:38:20,470 --> 00:38:21,380
George.

610
00:38:23,330 --> 00:38:24,270
George!

611
00:38:28,490 --> 00:38:29,520
George!

612
00:38:41,740 --> 00:38:42,900
Hello, father.

613
00:38:43,270 --> 00:38:44,580
Told you I'd get out.

614
00:38:45,980 --> 00:38:47,120
Yes, you did.

615
00:38:47,410 --> 00:38:49,070
I told you this weren't over.

616
00:38:50,390 --> 00:38:52,910
You'll be sold still, if the whores will have you.

617
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:55,270
I'm not going anywhere.

618
00:38:56,500 --> 00:38:57,350
You will.

619
00:38:57,380 --> 00:39:00,530
You will go where I tell you!

620
00:39:00,660 --> 00:39:01,820
I won't.

621
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:06,040
I won't. I --

622
00:39:15,820 --> 00:39:17,000
Please!

623
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,910
Henry Hopkins.

624
00:39:38,450 --> 00:39:39,510
What is this?

625
00:40:04,870 --> 00:40:05,740
Stephen.

626
00:40:06,710 --> 00:40:08,590
That's his name, the boy.

627
00:40:09,120 --> 00:40:10,480
He told you?

628
00:40:10,630 --> 00:40:11,490
Yep.

629
00:40:13,770 --> 00:40:15,540
Two years without speaking,

630
00:40:15,540 --> 00:40:17,660
and in one day, he tells you his name.

631
00:40:18,370 --> 00:40:20,800
He must have really taken to you, captain.

632
00:40:20,800 --> 00:40:22,230
No, I wouldn't say that.

633
00:40:22,230 --> 00:40:23,760
And who could blame him?

634
00:40:26,260 --> 00:40:27,660
Boys need attention

635
00:40:28,220 --> 00:40:31,710
and hard work to burn off their energy.

636
00:40:31,710 --> 00:40:32,980
And I'm grateful...

637
00:40:33,750 --> 00:40:35,320
for your hard work.

638
00:40:37,620 --> 00:40:39,350
It's the first hours passed since I've come back

639
00:40:39,350 --> 00:40:43,160
where I haven't thought about witches.

640
00:40:45,100 --> 00:40:47,300
I supposed one could choose that life --

641
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:52,840
Honest work, community, a loving family,

642
00:40:53,530 --> 00:40:55,680
and not a witch in sight.

643
00:40:56,490 --> 00:40:58,450
Maybe there's hope for us yet.

644
00:41:00,060 --> 00:41:00,940
You!

645
00:41:02,190 --> 00:41:03,710
Alert the selectmen.

646
00:41:03,710 --> 00:41:06,730
Another witch has been revealed. Follow me.

647
00:41:07,160 --> 00:41:08,350
Or maybe not.

648
00:41:09,560 --> 00:41:11,060
Mary Sibley!

649
00:41:15,640 --> 00:41:17,280
Your husband is awake.

650
00:41:27,030 --> 00:41:28,240
George is awake?

651
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:30,350
Has he spoken?

652
00:41:30,350 --> 00:41:33,080
He is rendered incapable of speech.

653
00:41:33,080 --> 00:41:37,810
Nevertheless, the name of his tormentor has been divulged.

654
00:41:37,810 --> 00:41:38,970
What does that mean --

655
00:41:39,930 --> 00:41:41,720
"Rendered unable to speak"?

656
00:41:43,030 --> 00:41:45,160
Do you recognize this potion?

657
00:41:45,250 --> 00:41:46,270
Yes.

658
00:41:46,730 --> 00:41:48,430
It's a physic for pain.

659
00:41:49,120 --> 00:41:51,290
I gave it to Isaac to give to Mr. Sibley.

660
00:41:51,290 --> 00:41:53,130
A physic for pain?

661
00:41:55,510 --> 00:41:58,350
Tell me, would a physic for pain

662
00:41:59,350 --> 00:42:02,700
seal Mr. Sibley's mouth shut...

663
00:42:03,650 --> 00:42:05,130
with a golden web?

664
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:23,230
A tonic for pain.

665
00:42:23,370 --> 00:42:24,500
Nothing more.

666
00:42:26,200 --> 00:42:27,740
Might I suggest, father,

667
00:42:27,880 --> 00:42:30,320
That Mrs. Sibley's tonic is just that,

668
00:42:31,280 --> 00:42:32,250
and the work of the web is due,

669
00:42:32,250 --> 00:42:35,920
more likely, to the real witch's spider familiar.

670
00:42:41,330 --> 00:42:42,240
Yes.

671
00:42:43,710 --> 00:42:45,830
It's a possibility. Search the house.

672
00:42:45,840 --> 00:42:46,720
Wait!

673
00:42:48,220 --> 00:42:49,250
I'm sorry, sir.

674
00:42:50,780 --> 00:42:52,110
Did you say a spider?

675
00:42:53,660 --> 00:42:57,520
The Lewis child, once tortured and possessed by witches.

676
00:42:57,520 --> 00:42:59,660
Yet now she looks remarkably well.

677
00:42:59,830 --> 00:43:01,820
All due to Mrs. Sibley's kindness.

678
00:43:03,150 --> 00:43:04,820
She saved my life.

679
00:43:05,360 --> 00:43:07,580
I was tortured and tormented,

680
00:43:07,760 --> 00:43:09,440
at the verge of begging for death,

681
00:43:09,440 --> 00:43:13,480
and Mary sibley delivered me from evil.

682
00:43:13,920 --> 00:43:16,280
Which is why I hesitate to say --

683
00:43:16,280 --> 00:43:18,940
What is it you have to say, girl?

684
00:43:19,110 --> 00:43:19,750
The other morning,

685
00:43:19,750 --> 00:43:23,520
when Mrs. Sibley was out on shipping business...

686
00:43:25,250 --> 00:43:28,350
- Yes? - ...I did pass Tituba's room,

687
00:43:29,040 --> 00:43:32,620
and she was doing the strangest thing.

688
00:43:32,620 --> 00:43:34,530
Tell us, Mercy. Tell us what you saw.

689
00:43:34,530 --> 00:43:37,430
She held a spider to her neck.

690
00:43:39,300 --> 00:43:40,170
Yes?

691
00:43:41,020 --> 00:43:41,980
Yes?

692
00:43:41,980 --> 00:43:44,100
She seemed to feed it.

693
00:43:46,830 --> 00:43:47,800
You.

694
00:43:49,280 --> 00:43:50,250
Come here.

695
00:44:01,790 --> 00:44:03,460
I hereby arrest you...

696
00:44:04,990 --> 00:44:07,700
on the charge of witchcraft.

697
00:44:07,790 --> 00:44:08,920
Guards.

698
00:44:08,990 --> 00:44:09,790
Yes, sir. 

699
00:44:09,800 --> 00:44:10,760
Aye, sir.

